Timespan = distinct int64

  self: int64

Lets

NANO_SECOND = Timespan(1)
MICRO_SECOND = 1000 * NANO_SECOND
MILLI_SECOND = 1000 * MICRO_SECOND
SECOND = 1000 * MILLI_SECOND
MINUTE = 60 * SECOND
HOUR = 60 * MINUTE
DAY = 24 * HOUR
